jective_endings")\'>adjective endings drills</a>.<br><sup>4</sup><i>Zeit</i> is a feminine singular noun.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>Zeit</i> is in the accusative case because it follows <i>f&uuml;r</i>, which is one of those <a href=German.html#=Prepositions=a target=German>German prepositions after which the accusative case is required</a>.',
